      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tomato paste</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Add 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
